## рҹҺҜ Project Overview

This Healthcare Management System demonstrates professional software development practices including:

- вң… **Object-Oriented Design** - Classes, encapsulation, inheritance
- вң… **MVC Architecture** - Models, Stores (Controllers), Logging (Views)
- вң… **CRUD Operations** - Complete data manipulation
- вң… **Exception Handling** - Custom exceptions for error management
- вң… **Logging System** - Comprehensive activity tracking
- вң… **Data Generation** - Realistic test data using Faker
- вң… **Type Hints** - Professional Python code standards

